    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so it's not a guaranteed win for the town. i'm just worried that it'll disproportionately hurt the little guys trying to start something new while the big chains can just absorb the cost. do you think these laws are fundamentally fair to small business owners, or are they mostly just helping out people regardless of the economic downside?",
